## Shipped files

### Server libs
- `server/lib/idx.js` — IDX.co.id proxy (profil, dividen tunai/saham,
  ESG, pemegang saham, financial report, calendar, perubahan nama,
  core business). 10-min cache + curated fallback list of 35 emiten.
- `server/lib/coingecko.js` — Top coins, coin detail, scam-risk heuristic
  (0-100 score from age, cap, volume, homepage, known scam list, 30d
  pump/dump).
- `server/lib/insurance.js` — Curated dataset: BPJS, Prudential, AIA,
  Allianz, Manulife, Sinar Mas, Asuransi Astra (Garda Oto), AXA Mandiri.
  Premium calculator + recommendation engine.
- `server/lib/db.js` — better-sqlite3 layer with in-memory fallback.
  Tables: user, health_snapshot, holding, buffer.
- `server/integrations/telegram.js` — Polling bot, env-gated, commands:
  /start /help /score /quote /crypto /emiten /ask /portofolio.

### Server endpoints
- `/api/idx/emiten` — list emiten
- `/api/idx/profile/:code`, `/api/idx/dividen/:code`,
  `/api/idx/financial/:code`, `/api/idx/esg/:code`,
  `/api/idx/pemegang/:code`, `/api/idx/calendar/:code`
- `/api/idx/:code` — composite overview
- `/api/crypto/top`, `/api/crypto/coin`, `/api/crypto/risk`
- `/api/insurance`, `/api/insurance/:id`,
  `/api/insurance/premium`, `/api/insurance/recommend`
- `/api/me/portfolio` (GET), `/api/me/portfolio/holding` (POST/DELETE),
  `/api/me/portfolio/buffer` (POST)
- `/api/me/health` (POST), `/api/me/health/history` (GET)

### Agent tools (registered)
- `get_idx_company`, `get_idx_dividen`, `get_idx_financial`,
  `list_idx_emiten`
- `get_crypto_quote`, `assess_crypto_scam_risk`
- `list_insurance_companies`, `calculate_insurance_premium`,
  `recommend_insurance`

### Frontend pages (new)
- `src/pages/CekEmiten.tsx` — IDX browser + emiten profile bento
- `src/pages/CryptoWatch.tsx` — top coins + risk panel + market table
- `src/pages/Asuransi.tsx` — comparator + premium calc + recommender
- `src/pages/Portofolio.tsx` — holdings + buffer manager (localStorage)

### Routing & nav
- `src/main.tsx` — routes for /emiten, /crypto, /asuransi,
  /portofolio, /kesehatan
- `src/components/Layout.tsx` — home (/) hides nav, shows floating logo
  only. Bento grid serves as primary navigation. Other pages keep
  minimal sticky header.

### Docs (new)
- `CLAUDE.md` — canonical agent brief
- `AGENTS.md` — non-Claude agent capabilities summary
- `CONTRIBUTING.md` — branch/commit/test rules
- `ARCHITECTURE.md` — diagram + data flow
- `DEPLOYMENT.md` — Sumopod / Jetorbit / generic VPS / Docker recipes

### Tests
- `tests/server/health.test.js` — 5 cases
- `tests/server/extras.test.js` — 7 cases (insurance + crypto-risk)
- All 32 tests passing.

